				<li>Commission= Commission (Per Lot) × Volume</li>
				<li>Swap Fee= Swap Long/short Points × Volume × Contract Size × Point Size* × Days</li>
				<li>*The point size depends on the decimal digits of each CFD Instrument.</li>
				<li>Point Size for 5 decimal digits = 0.00001</li>
				<li>Point Size for 3 decimal digits = 0.001</li>
				<li>Point Size for 2 decimal digits = 0.01</li>
				<li>Point Size for 1 decimal digits = 0.1</li>
				<li>Convesrion fee= market exchange rate + fee</li>
			</ul>
