				provides a service and acts investor faith, asking to be compensated for any transaction
				with the “spread”, the difference between the price BID and ASK price on the currency pair
				that is traded. The broker adds the spread within the trade price and keeps for himself by
				covering the costs of management and obtaining a revenue.
			</p>
			<p class="text-color mb-6">
